# SWAY notes
2021-08-01


grim - screenshot taker for wayland; only command-line version??
slurp - select a region in wayland and print it to stdout. works well with grim

kanshi - dynamic display profiles; equivalent for autoandr

mako - lightweight wayland notification daemon

rofi - window switcher, application launcher, dmenu replacement

sway
swaybg
swayidle
swaylock

waybar

wlroots
xdg-desktop-portal-wlr
   wlroots backend
   
   in sway cfg:
     exec dbus-update-activation-environment --systemd WAYLAND_DISPLAY XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP=sway

   in gdm desktop
     sudo vim /usr/share/wayland-sessions/sway.desktop      
     X-GDM-SessionRegisters=true
    
   if not showing up -> NVIDIA prorietary driver does not support wayland

